隔離有股氣 <br />\n我老婆啤住我 <br />\n話「隻鹿咁得意你都撞死佢！」 <br />\n就走左入房&hellip;依家嬲左我&hellip; <br />\n<br />\n我去哄佢 <br />\n佢叫我應承佢以後玩gta要遵守交通規則&hellip;做良好市民 <br />\n唔可以衝紅燈&hellip;偷車&hellip;殺人&hellip;同埋撞死小動物etc&hellip; <br />\n先比我繼續玩&hellip; <br />\n好撚慘啊&hellip;早知唔撞死隻鹿啦 <br />\n屌你老母死人鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65f9486f0cffa0ca23f229864ac9ac264bcb43d","tid":139074,"uid":18044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"值得買 值得玩 線上游戲"},{"pid":"72d6884cbdd051405c1778e20167f4f56d040111","tid":139074,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買部薄版囉<br />\n其實PS4又可以睇netflix又播到blue ray係抵屌<br />\n500GB先二千幾蚊</blockquote><br />\n唔係二千有找咩"},{"pid":"769776b53b374e13bf8ca13716681005daa51368","tid":139074,"uid":2621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"買完唔止淨係玩GTA，你會留意有咩game 出實有一隻岩心水，況且你去隔離post買二手game玩完再放返出去等於唔洗錢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我同班frd 由ps3 出GTA玩到一齊出部ps4繼續玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 淨係賽車日日DL 啲新圖落黎玩都玩左幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}